snippet.title: Moonleap - Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Help our moon boy on his journey to recover shooting stars in this innovative puzzle platformer 🌜✨

A full version of Moonleap is coming for PC, IOS, Android and more!

Wishlist now on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2166050/Moonleap/
